      "time_str": "00:11.500",
      "text": "被爱伤害以后",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 14.74,
      "time_str": "00:14.740",
      "text": "你曾说的每一句爱我到头",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 18.6,
